'''德拉弗拉塔'''（{{lang-it|De La Fratta}}）是[[聖馬力諾三塔|聖馬力諾三塔]]之一，另外兩座是[[蒙塔萊_(聖馬力諾)|蒙塔萊]]和[[瓜伊塔|瓜伊塔]]。德拉弗拉塔位於蒂塔諾山的山頂，內部是一個博物館<ref>{{cite web|title=Museum of Historical Weapons|url=http://www.zainoo.com/en/italy/emilia-romagna/san-marino/museum-of-historical-weapons|website=www.zainoo.com|accessdate=2 March 2015|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402133146/http://www.zainoo.com/en/italy/emilia-romagna/san-marino/museum-of-historical-weapons|dead-url=yes}}</ref> It was constructed in the 13th century on the remains of an older Roman fort.<ref>{{cite web|title=Second Tower (Cesta)|url=http://www.visitsanmarino.com/on-line/en/home/experience/arts-and-culture/scheda31097701.html|website=www.visitsanmarino.com|accessdate=2 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224358/http://www.visitsanmarino.com/on-line/en/home/experience/arts-and-culture/scheda31097701.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
